<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>四川红油鸳鸯龙骨锅底</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201201/d3cd65c9fb7846d5b7d30ccc15ef90b3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
